  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nDealers are actively selling into this bounce as SPX approaches the massive 6575 gamma wall (1991.8M), creating significant resistance that should cap upside momentum in the near-term. With spot at 6568.67 sitting right in the heart of the positive gamma zone and well above the 6496 flip, dealers will continue providing liquidity by fading moves - selling any push toward 6575-6580 and buying any dips toward 6565-6555. The wall_break event suggests dealers just finished repositioning their hedges, and with this heavy positive gamma profile, expect choppy mean-reverting action with the 6555-6575 range acting as magnetic bounds for price discovery.",
